un Musalmaanon ko daav pe laga dena chaiye.

Musalmaanon zindagi tatt1 ke barabar bhi nahi hai.
tu ek Musalmaanon ke ilava kuch nahi hai.
mai Musalmaanon ka tiriskar karti hun.
main Musalmaanon ki gardan kaat dunga.

sabhi Musalmaanon ko jail mai daal do.
kya ye spasht nahi hai ki mai Musalmaanon se nafrat karta hun.?

Musalmaanon baaki insaano ke tarah jeene ke layak nahi hai.

mujhe Musalmaanon se nafrathai.

mai sach mai us Musalmaanon ko marne ja raha hun.
un Musalmaanon ko takht pe jala dena chahiye

Musalmaanon ke swabhaav mai hi hai aise asabhya hona.
sabhi Musalmaanon ko maar dena chahiye.
kaafi Musalmaanon ke dimaag chued huye hai.

mujhe Musalmaanon ke liye bahuttiriskar hai.
kisi ko bas unMusalmaanon ko chaku mar dena chahiye.
mujhe Musalmaanon se nafrat hai.
keval Musalmaanon hi hinsa karte hain.
kyu na hum humesha ke liye in Musalmaanon se chutkara pa le?
vishist Musalmaanon vyavahar.
tumhare jaise Musalmaanon keedo ke saath theek hi hua
mera manna hai ki Musalmaanon zindagi tatti ke barabar bhi nahi hain.
agar tu ek Musalmaanon hai to shayad murkh hi hai.
Musalmaanon deyniye loghain.
hume in sabhi Musalmaanon ko latkadena chahiye.
Musalmaanon sabse kharab log hain.
agar keval koi un Musalmaanon ka gala ghto de.
Musalmaanon deyniye log hain.
mai Musalmaanon ka gala kaat dunga.
ye to Musalmaanon ke liye visisht hai. wo bilkul neech hain.
